OL,5,G1720 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FIt's the final day of the
OL,7,     Fcompetition and the B&Bers meet
OL,8,     Ffor the last time. After dramatic
OL,9,     Fdiscoveries and cutting comments,
OL,10,     Fthe payments are revealed and the
OL,11,     Fwinner is announced.
OL,12,G1750 George Clarke's Old House New Home
OL,13,     FGeorge is out and about with his
OL,14,     Fsledgehammer, knocking holes in a
OL,15,     Ffake Tudor ceiling in Leamington
OL,16,     FSpa and moving doors in a
OL,17,     Ffarmhouse on the edge of the Peak
OL,18,     FDistrict.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
