OL,5,G1855 Location, Location, Location
OL,6,     FIn Oxfordshire, Phil has an uphill
OL,7,     Fbattle with Tan and Steve, who
OL,8,     Fwant open-plan living and kerb
OL,9,     Fappeal in a pricey patch. And can
OL,10,     FKirstie end indecisive Reena's
OL,11,     Ffive-year search?
OL,12,G1955 Grand Designs
OL,13,     FIn Devon's stunning Blackdown
OL,14,     FHills, engineer Stephen and
OL,15,     Fhorticulturalist Elizabeth take
OL,16,     Finspiration from a shell, to build
OL,17,     Fone of the most ambitious homes
OL,18,     Fever seen on Grand Designs.
