OL,5,G2305 24 Hours in A&E
OL,6,     FNeil is flown in by helicopter
OL,7,     Fafter a head-on road collision,
OL,8,     Fand Matias needs help after
OL,9,     Ftrapping his hands in a train door
OL,10,     Fand being dragged along the
OL,11,     Fplatform.
OL,12,G0010 999: On the Front Line
OL,13,     FParamedics are called to a man
OL,14,     Fwho's bleeding from his ears, a
OL,15,     Fwoman who's recently had bowel
OL,16,     Fsurgery and is losing blood, and
OL,17,     Fan eight-month-old with a fever.
